snippet.title: WARSHIFT Gameplay - Winter Storm Environment Test
snippet.description:
This is a new WARSHIFT gameplay map Winter Storm on which I'm currently working. This large spacious game level has a lot of flat surfaces for base development and battles. It is not completely finished, it's just a test of winter environment. But you already can feel its atmosphere.

Purchase WARSHIFT on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/392580
